## Tables

```ermd-table
physicalName: Author
id: tbl_mpsaezq4_4mvq2
logicalName: Author
comment: Stores book authors — composite PK on Name+Address
designNote: Author and Address together uniquely identify an author
columns:
  - physicalName: Name
    id: col_mpsaezq4_frk88
    logicalName: Name
    dictionaryId: dict_mpsaezq4_gdera
    isPrimaryKey: true
    isNullable: false
    defaultValue: null
    comment: Author full name (part of composite PK)
    designNote: Name alone is not unique — composite key needed
  - physicalName: Address
    id: col_mpsaezq4_vbo8i
    logicalName: Address
    dictionaryId: dict_mpsaezq4_gdera
    isPrimaryKey: true
    isNullable: false
    defaultValue: null
    comment: Author postal address (part of composite PK)
    designNote: Part of composite PK with Name
  - physicalName: URL
    id: col_mpsaezq4_91l5v
    logicalName: URL
    dictionaryId: dict_mpsaezq4_4iqzt
    isPrimaryKey: false
    isNullable: true
    defaultValue: null
    comment: Author personal or publisher website
```

